# ============================================================
# INPTIC DevOps - Configuration Environnement
# ============================================================
# IMPORTANT: Ne commitez JAMAIS ce fichier avec des vraies valeurs !
# Utilisez des mots de passe forts en production.
# ============================================================

# ── PostgreSQL Database ─────────────────────────────────────
POSTGRES_USER=inptic_user
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=changeme_postgres_password_2024
POSTGRES_DB=inptic_db
POSTGRES_HOST=db
POSTGRES_PORT=5432

# ── Application Flask ───────────────────────────────────────
SECRET_KEY=changeme_secret_key_very_long_and_random_string_here
FLASK_ENV=production
FLASK_DEBUG=0
APP_PORT=5000

# ── Email Configuration (SMTP) ──────────────────────────────
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=votre.email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASSWORD=changeme_app_password_gmail
SMTP_USE_TLS=true

# Emails de notification
ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@example.com
NOTIFICATION_EMAIL=notifications@example.com

# ── Grafana ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
GRAFANA_ADMIN_USER=admin
GRAFANA_ADMIN_PASSWORD=changeme_grafana_admin_password
GRAFANA_PORT=3001

# Configuration Grafana avancée
GF_SECURITY_ADMIN_USER=admin
GF_SECURITY_ADMIN_PASSWORD=admin
GF_AUTH_ANONYMOUS_ENABLED=false
GF_USERS_ALLOW_SIGN_UP=false
GF_USERS_ALLOW_ORG_CREATE=false
GF_INSTALL_PLUGINS=

# ── Jenkins ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
JENKINS_ADMIN_USER=admin
JENKINS_ADMIN_PASSWORD=changeme_jenkins_admin_password
JENKINS_PORT=8080
JENKINS_AGENT_PORT=50000

# Configuration Jenkins
JENKINS_OPTS=--prefix=/jenkins
JAVA_OPTS=-Djenkins.install.runSetupWizard=false -Xmx2g

# ── Prometheus ──────────────────────────────────────────────
PROMETHEUS_PORT=9090
PROMETHEUS_RETENTION_TIME=15d
PROMETHEUS_SCRAPE_INTERVAL=15s

# ── Alertmanager ────────────────────────────────────────────
ALERTMANAGER_PORT=9093

# Configuration des alertes email
ALERTMANAGER_SMTP_FROM=alertmanager@example.com
ALERTMANAGER_SMTP_TO=admin@example.com
ALERTMANAGER_SMTP_SMARTHOST=smtp.gmail.com:587
ALERTMANAGER_SMTP_AUTH_USERNAME=votre.email@gmail.com
ALERTMANAGER_SMTP_AUTH_PASSWORD=changeme_app_password_gmail

# ── PostgreSQL Exporter ─────────────────────────────────────
POSTGRES_EXPORTER_PORT=9187
DATA_SOURCE_NAME=postgresql://inptic_user:changeme_postgres_password_2024@db:5432/inptic_db?sslmode=disable

# ── Monitoring & Métriques ──────────────────────────────────
METRICS_ENABLED=true
METRICS_PORT=5000

# ── Sécurité ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Clé pour JWT (si utilisé)
JWT_SECRET_KEY=changeme_jwt_secret_key_very_long_random_string

# Session
SESSION_COOKIE_SECURE=false
SESSION_COOKIE_HTTPONLY=true
SESSION_COOKIE_SAMESITE=Lax

# ── Logs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
LOG_FORMAT=json

# ── Backup ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
BACKUP_ENABLED=true
BACKUP_RETENTION_DAYS=7

# ── Réseau ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
NETWORK_NAME=monitoring

# ── Timezone ────────────────────────────────────────────────
TZ=Africa/Kinshasa

# ── GitHub/GitLab (pour Jenkins CI/CD) ─────────────────────
GIT_REPO_URL=https://github.com/Herlymba828/inptic-etudiants.git
GIT_BRANCH=main
GIT_USERNAME=
GIT_TOKEN=

# ── Docker Registry (optionnel) ─────────────────────────────
DOCKER_REGISTRY_URL=
DOCKER_REGISTRY_USERNAME=
DOCKER_REGISTRY_PASSWORD=

# ── Feature Flags ───────────────────────────────────────────
ENABLE_REGISTRATION=true
ENABLE_EMAIL_VERIFICATION=true
ENABLE_TWO_FACTOR_AUTH=false

# ── Limites & Performance ───────────────────────────────────
MAX_UPLOAD_SIZE=10485760
REQUEST_TIMEOUT=30
MAX_WORKERS=4
WORKER_CONNECTIONS=1000

# ── URLs Externes (pour webhooks, callbacks) ────────────────
EXTERNAL_URL=http://localhost:5000
JENKINS_URL=http://localhost:8080
GRAFANA_URL=http://localhost:3000
PROMETHEUS_URL=http://localhost:9090
